	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Can someone explain how or who gets the most (or least, for that matter) debt in a near-wipe...first man down? last man down? survivors? <br />
<br />
From what I've read and heard, the debt isn't spread equally among group members, but I haven't been able to find a definitive answer to this anywhere.<br />
<br />
Thanks,<br />
Glaani<br />
Guk Server</p>
	
	
	
	
	
