	<p>My gut feeling is that WoW appeals to those who miss early EQ days when the game was more high fantasy and more stylized. And that EQ 2 appeals to those who feel like EQ1 has grown stale and they want something fresher and more modern. But I know generalizations are not valid over everyone, just saying it seems to be a trend among people I know.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
