	<!-- message -->
	<p>*shrugs*<br />
<br />
I am in EQ 2 because of the game immersion. WoW looks cartoonish to me.<br />
<br />
Both games have personal appeal to different people.  Some will think that EQ 2 is visually more appealing, while others will feel that way about WoW.  Some will swear the EQ 2 is dumbed down, while others will say the same thing about WoW game play.<br />
<br />
Whatever you want to find great about each game is there, as well as whatever you want to find wrong.<br />
<br />
I just hope that whatever game people end up playing that they enjoy and leave the rest of us to enjoy whatever game we have decided to play without all the: U sux cuz u play (insert whatever game you aren't playing here) and other random insults for no apparent reason that have been plaguing sites for all the games.<br />
<br />
To each their own and all.</p>
	
	
	
