1. And this happened to me. Party in Stormhold, full group we wipe due to a bad pull. When u release u end up outside stormhold, ok np zone back in ........ummm I am in but group is still grayed out. Oh they are in Stormhold2 I am in stormhold3. Cant reach group so can't get any debt payed back, suck up 113% debt have a nice day. And I thought this game was beta tested? I myself hope they fix this one or else your on your own in some zones. <br />
