	<!-- message -->
	<p>Your point number one has nothing to do with debt, but a (depending on your point of view) bug with how players are placed in zones with multiple instances.  I personally feel this is a bug, and that members of the same party should ALWAYS be placed in the same instance of a zone.<br />
<br />
Point three, you are wrong.  The difference is that you see greater debt until you recover your shard.  Let's say my party wipes.  I have a HUGE debt at the point we all revive.  Now, a HUGE portion of that debt will be repaid - as soon as I recover *my* shard.<br />
<br />
Sounds to me like you simply need a little more experience with the system yet.  There may yet be bugs in it, real programming bugs, but I've not seen any.  I managed to get killed 5 times in Stormhold in a 2 hour span, but never saw anything that I can say was a programming type bug.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
