	<p><blockquote><span class="smallfont">Quote:</span><hr size="1" />Originally Posted by <b>Sudedor</b><br /><i>Actually I do.<br />
<br />
You need an INT caster who has Invis and willing to help you.  Seems that EQ2, unlike EQLive,  doesn't make a distinction between alive and undead when Invis is considered.<br />
