On the other hand, Fallen gate should allow the "click on entrance" to recover your shard. Not sure if it was mentioned in this thread or some other.<br />
<br />
The easiest way to recover a shard is to find someone a few levels higher. Chances are that the mobs will turn grey to you when grouped with him. Still I think that there should be mechanisms to summon shards, like summon corpse, or drag corpses. Otherwise a dungeon crawl can become a very unpleasant experience.<br />
 <br />
At level 20+ a group wipe gives me about one bubble (10%) of debt, and it takes at least one hour in a decent group to get out of that. I find the shared debt system to be unnecessary. A priest that lets the tank die is kicked out of group fast, as well as any other char who does not pull his weight. Such a someone is already hurting the group because everyone gets less exp and less loot, thats enough of a penalty.</p>
	
	
	
		<div>__________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=380885" target="_blank">Shismar Tarrasiz</a> <br />
Scaled Prophet <br />
Shining Alliance, Prexus</div>
	
	
