<br />
96% Exp rez = You lose ~1% or less than you started with. (I've been 10% into level, been killed, rezzed and came back still at 10% into level)<br />
<br />
The other difference is if you have people that give you a share of their exp loss death then release.<br />
<br />
When people release they don't share in YOUR death, meaning you could wind up theoretically with almost 2 full deaths of debt. (11/6ths)<br />
<br />
Not that I care, because it doesn't bother me a whole lot. I just wanted to bring up some inconsistencies in the math there.</p>
	
	
	
