	<p>I've died to a train in Blackburrow before where I clicked on the door and got the message "Please select an instance" I selected one and got the message "That instance is full, please select another" but I died shortly after getting that message.<br />
<br />
When I went to retrieve my shard it was in Antonica, so I'm thinking even though the person was still IN Vermin's Snye when they died, since they were in the "Pick an instance" interface it considered them to be in the other zone, even though it was mobs in the prior zone that killed them.<br />
<br />
It's kinda mind boggling how the process works, but I think that's the general idea.</p>
	
	
	
