	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Yes. Exp debt is removed by 1% per hour you are offline.<br />
<br />
So you can just not play and get your debt paid off that way as well.<br />
<br />
Actually I think it's been mentioned in some other threads, but it's a valid point to add to this thread.<br />
<br />
It's kinda nice.<br />
<br />
One thing to add, Exp debt doesn't reduce if you put yourself in trader mode.</p>
	
	
	
